{"tid":1198440,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"6.9證實左「今天我」係無用 「揸緊中指」先可以成功","createTime":"2019-06-10T08:41:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T09:05:29.000Z","uid":204481,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c86be6b55598f79dce6e42693da160a47e964073","tid":1198440,"uid":204481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T08:41:07.000Z","msg":"一直都知自由係要去捍衛<br />\n不惜一切就算我哋依然處於弱勢<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">百萬人上街又點</span><br />\n<br />\n奸商加狗官最叻係玩拑制<br />\n事實擺在眼前就咪玩抹黑矇閉<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">6.9朝早極和平 凌晨一有衝突就被抹黑成暴動</span><br />\n<br />\n強勢未倒下 頭顱未被斬下<br />\n有法治一日我哋依然不怕<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">逃犯條例過左 仲有法治?</span><br />\n<br />\n一二兩隻手指 二 二就只有自由兩個字<br />\n一無所有嘅鬥士 揸緊中指唔係你想咁易<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">幾多香港人有家屋 做義士真係唔易<br />\n大家更加要支持願意行出黎嘅戰友<br />\n真係唔係想像中咁易</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我並唔認同你講嘅一切一切<br />\n但我會捍衛 即使死不眼閉<br />\n並唔認為你所謂嘅需要克制<br />\n會帶來公平 穩定壓倒一切<br />\n唔屈服於錢幣 唔怕照肺<br />\n見權貴一樣照吠 正義係不顧一切<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">正義係不顧一切</span><br />\n<br />\n你不要放棄 堅持到尾<br />\n自由要接棒 我哋要靠晒你哋<br />\n不管犧牲幾多 揸緊中指我道理<br />\n不自由無寧死 妥協最後 失敗者只會係你<br />\n犧牲幾多 揸緊中指我道理<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">經歷佔中 旺角 6.9嘅失敗 大家唔好放棄 自由係要接棒 靠我地爭取落去</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">聽聽下真係好感慨</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">6.11約定大家出黎不見不散 誓師硬頂惡法</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XgKazvhNYz8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXgKazvhNYz8&d=AePTNAtL1N4PdcNq2S6jCMdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=42c54b64\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XgKazvhNYz8</a>"},{"pid":"706640b6d1e9f7062ae8fb43f9037fdc45fbac27","tid":1198440,"uid":204481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T08:42:34.000Z","msg":"大家記住6.9嘅失敗 6.11企出黎  話比政府知我地唔係羔羊"},{"pid":"61becbf623f2dd5c5f81ca86d2e9d7cff1e9a0b8","tid":1198440,"uid":204481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T08:43:22.000Z","msg":"希望大家出到黎唔好再淨係打卡唱k 要做實事"},{"pid":"fe9074ad9d2809abc680c874f240fdebb64cef1a","tid":1198440,"uid":204481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T08:45:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k17FDwt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk17FDwt.png&h=44eca623&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89673d9383128af06a6facdfb200e8254b80a090","tid":1198440,"uid":204481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T08:47:34.000Z","msg":"「今天我」對政府已經無用 我地嘅政府就係咁無恥<br />\n係時候「揸緊中指」"},{"pid":"7e390ad4ed6b8c53b4c758032d14e2478fce0e25","tid":1198440,"uid":204481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T08:50:09.000Z","msg":"有家室要返工嘅 希望你地放工都可以黎支援<br />\n盡一個作為香港人嘅責任"},{"pid":"5d6b6fa08bb348960f84b120a416399ddef19da8","tid":1198440,"uid":204481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T08:52:36.000Z","msg":"推到唔再唱今天我"},{"pid":"44b4b38f279308903cc061cbcfa99e13fe1b376d","tid":1198440,"uid":204481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T08:55:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0281dbb557bec3c351a9c07b2b828c4bf80bfa4","tid":1198440,"uid":204481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T08:56:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1nMSuGV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1nMSuGV.png&h=9ca51882&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"120e0fb20c34b7d33d793e53bc689610ff52e768","tid":1198440,"uid":204481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:02:00.000Z","msg":"就算唔衝嘅巴打都可以去做後援 物資 <br />\n記住 你唔去 我唔去 就無人去<br />\n他日香港淪陷 你一定後悔"},{"pid":"99aeafe03944c4569e89ea4265dc27ad9d2bf0cb","tid":1198440,"uid":204481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:02:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9cd59a19e5e72600fa9f3f598e5a9be48d128165","tid":1198440,"uid":204481,"like":0,"dislike